social_posts.post_text: I don’t go out much anymore but when something as special as this comes along respect should be given . A beautiful evening celebrating the life of Madison Bubiski . Beautiful butterflies 🦋 were released in her honor at the Houston Museum of Natural Science in the Cockrell Butterfly Center . Richard who doesn’t like his name on anything and prefers to do things privately, was so moved he purchased 100 🦋even though they didn’t have that many for release he said when you do it for Madi . Beautiful Madison lost her life attending the Astroworld Travis Scott concert. May we never forget those who passed in such a tragic way . Thank you Edward Sanchez for putting this special night together for us . #pinkbowsfoundation @zimmermann @maisonvalentino @louboutinworld @escbeauty
